<h3>
	Mombasa &nbsp;by Head Porter
</h3>
<p>
	日本包袋品牌 Head Porter 重新推出动物印花包 Mombasa，灵感源于肯尼亚草原上的野生动物，用人造纤维防造出豹子的纹路。有黑白色和黄棕色两组。这一系列涵盖了背包、挎包、手提包等多种样式。<a href="http://store.headporter.co.jp/en/products/detail.php?product_id=2448" target="_blank">这里是购买链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/aa55e98ee162.jpg" width="500" height="295" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/c17ae5c8bcdc.jpg" width="1080" height="1080" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
